snippet.title: Highway Acceleroid Booster - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
hello thank you for being interested in my oc, she is very strong and prety and could take on dr. sigma xx and hyperbass.exe at the same time.

ZDoom topic: https://forum.zdoom.org/viewtopic.php?f=43&t=66819
Doomworld topic: https://www.doomworld.com/forum/topic/111081-gameplay-mod-highway-acceleroid-booster-v1-life-in-the-fast-lane/
Dropbox: https://www.dropbox.com/s/3vm92o52jz1y3hc/HighwayAcceleroidBooster-v1.pk3?dl=1
Google: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1N00BH2IbfWSXjP2ij00oA1navw7EzYcn/view?usp=sharing
Itch.io: https://terminusest13.itch.io/highway-acceleroid-booster

Music used:
Mega Man X - Opening Stage (Eurobeat Remix by Dominic Ninmark)
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OfLDM1jibso

Maps used (in order):
Obstacle Course - Map04
Megaman 8-Bit Deathmatch - GutsDozer
Jumpmaze - map13
RocketJump Xtreme - map06
Jenesis - Map12
BLDSTLP - Map02
Biowar - Map03
Dark Tartarus - Map10
Dark Tartarus - Map20
Lunatic - Map01 (with Rampancy.pk3)
Alienated - Map03
Dark Tartarus - Map13
Equinox - Map09
